metadata.name: Birth of power
metadata.description:
Be strong. 
Be original. 
Be yourself. 
Be the Power. 
Trust. 
Be not afraid.
share warmth with your loved ones and get energy you need.


We can handle any problem, be strong, be independent.
But sometimes we need a helping hand from the people we love. Just trust. Be not afraid.
Share warmth with your loved ones and get energy you need.

Digital drawing. Exclusive
